reviewText: This DVD is a great way to get into a fantastic, blood pressure lowering activity. Even if you are in decent health, the excersises on this video can help you enjoy a better quality of living. Personally, I find this revitalizing. This is great for reducing stress as well. The good doctor's intentions are very positive.
This is very easy to follow, I just don't use it enough . Many different levels to go. I would recommend
